  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in the donabe over medium heat.",
    "Add onion, celery, and carrot, sauté until onions are translucent.",
    "Stir in potatoes and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add mustard and stir to coat vegetables evenly.",
    "Pour in vegetable broth and grapefruit juice, bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Cover the donabe and simmer for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt, pepper, and fresh dill, then simmer for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Sprinkle toasted rye crumbs over the stew and serve hot."
